---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — OperatorStack"
  description="OperatorStack's full affiliate disclosure policy."
>
  <div style="background:var(--gray-50); border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray-200); padding:3rem 1.5rem 2.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:680px; margin:0 auto;">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p style="color:var(--gray-600); margin-top:.75rem;">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" style="padding-top:2.5rem;">
    <div class="content-width">
      <div class="prose">
        <p>OperatorStack participates in affiliate marketing programs. This means we earn a commission when you click certain links on this site and make a purchase or sign up for a service — at no additional cost to you.</p>

        <h2>What This Means</h2>
        <p>Some links on OperatorStack are affiliate links. When you click these links and sign up for a product, we receive a commission from the company. This is how we fund the site and keep our content free.</p>

        <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial coverage. We only recommend products we have personally evaluated and believe provide genuine value for multi-location operators. If a product has significant flaws, we include them in our reviews regardless of affiliate status.</p>

        <p>We never accept payment in exchange for positive reviews, and we never adjust ratings based on commission rates.</p>

        <h2>Programs We Participate In</h2>
        <p>OperatorStack participates in affiliate programs including but not limited to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>GoHighLevel Affiliate Program</li>
          <li>ConvertKit (Kit) Partner Program</li>
          <li>Thinkific Affiliate Program</li>
          <li>Kinsta Affiliate Program</li>
          <li>AWeber Affiliate Program</li>
          <li>HubSpot Affiliate Program</li>
          <li>Zapier Partner Program</li>
          <li>Amazon Associates Program</li>
          <li>Other SaaS and software affiliate programs</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
        <p>This disclosure is made in accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's guidelines on endorsements and testimonials (16 CFR Part 255). We are committed to transparency in all affiliate relationships.</p>

        <h2>Questions?</h2>
        <p>Our editorial process is independent of affiliate relationships. Recommendations are based on direct use and operator experience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
